             was indicted for <rs id="t18230115-24-off142" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18230115-24-off142" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230115-24-off142" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18230115-24-cd143" type="crimeDate">31st of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230115-24-off142 t18230115-24-cd143"></join>, a handkerchief, value 5 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18230115-24-victim300" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Sharpless
                        <interp inst="t18230115-24-victim300" type="surname" value="Sharpless"></interp>
